{"hash":"253751b2067367ef5ddfdde881310623e937cd4c","data":{"post":{"title":"文法","date":"December 20, 2021","content":"<h1 id=\"construction-dune-phrase\"><a href=\"#construction-dune-phrase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link heading-anchor\"></span></a>Construction d'une phrase</h1>\n<p>Sujet + Particule | Complément + Particule | Verbe (+ きだ)</p>\n<h2 id=\"phrase-nominale\"><a href=\"#phrase-nominale\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link heading-anchor\"></span></a>Phrase nominale</h2>\n<h3 id=\"affirmative-は--です\"><a href=\"#affirmative-%E3%81%AF--%E3%81%A7%E3%81%99\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link heading-anchor\"></span></a>Affirmative は + です</h3>\n<p>私 <strong>は</strong> デルフィン <strong>です</strong> / Je m'appelle Delphine</p>\n<p>日本 <strong>は</strong> 国 <strong>です</strong> / Le Japon est un pays</p>\n<h3 id=\"interrogative-は--か\"><a href=\"#interrogative-%E3%81%AF--%E3%81%8B\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link heading-anchor\"></span></a>Interrogative は + か</h3>\n<p>日本 <strong>は</strong> 国 <strong>ですか</strong> / Le Japon est un pays ?</p>\n<h2 id=\"phrase-verbale\"><a href=\"#phrase-verbale\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link heading-anchor\"></span></a>Phrase verbale</h2>\n<h3 id=\"affirmative-ます\"><a href=\"#affirmative-%E3%81%BE%E3%81%99\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link heading-anchor\"></span></a>Affirmative ます</h3>\n","tags":[{"title":"Grammaire","path":"/tag/Grammaire/"}]}},"context":{}}